        <div class="homePTag rounded">
            <h2>Next Steps</h2>
            <p>
                I have been living in Detroit for almost 5 years at this point and have started to enjoy calling it home. I come from
                a poor and also diverse part of the country, that gave me a lot of perspective on the world, something I didn't notice as much
